* [a9s Consul DNS](https://network.pivotal.io/products/a9s-consul) for PCF, v1.0.0 or later
* [a9s BOSH](https://network.pivotal.io/products/a9s-bosh) for PCF, v1.0.0 or later

For more information, see [Installing and Configuring a9s MySQL for PCF](./installing.html).

